OL,3,CMan, 59, arrested after woman sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted near M1 services
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof attempted rape after a woman was
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted near the M1
OL,9,Fservices at Leicester Forest East in
OL,10,FLeicestershire.
OL,12,FPolice say the woman, who is in her
OL,13,F20s, was grabbed from behind by a man
OL,14,Fwhile she was walking along Baines
OL,15,FLane towards Hinckley Road.
OL,17,FShe was reportedly pulled to the
OL,18,Fground and sexually assaulted. When
OL,19,Fshe began shouting for help, the man
OL,20,Fran off towards the southbound
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
