OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777482354
OL,3,CMan, 59, arrested after woman sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted near M1 services
OL,6,FA 59-year-old man is being questioned
OL,7,Fby police and remains in custody.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Jenny Tattersall
OL,10,Ffrom Leicestershire Police said: "I'd
OL,11,Flike to thank everyone who has come
OL,12,Fforward with information and supported
OL,13,Four enquiries to date.
OL,15,F"While we've made an arrest, our
OL,16,Finvestigation is still very much
OL,17,Fcontinuing. I'd urge anyone who can
OL,18,Fhelp but has not yet spoken to police
OL,19,Fto come forward.
OL,26,@rD@bOUwD@AOU
