OL,3,CMan, 59, arrested after woman sexually
OL,4,Cassaulted near M1 services
OL,6,F"We know anyone using the services may
OL,7,Fhave travelled from outside
OL,8,FLeicestershire and I'm appealing for
OL,9,FHGV drivers and other drivers who
OL,10,Fstopped there between 4pm and 7pm to
OL,11,Fget in touch."
OL,13,FPolice have set up a public portal
OL,14,Fwhere anyone can upload dashcam
OL,15,Ffootage or provide information
OL,16,Fdirectly to the investigation team:
OL,17,Fhttps://mipp.police.uk/operation/
OL,18,F33EM26I77-PO1
